SIMPLE: unconformable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unconformable
<hw>Un`con*form"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not conformable; not agreeable; not conforming.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Moral evil is an action <qex>unconformable</qex> to it [the rule
of our duty].</q> <rj><qau>I. Watts.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>Not conformable; not lying in a
parallel position; <as>as, <ex>unconformable</ex> strata</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`con*form"a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Un`con*form"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unconformist</ent>⟦br⟧
